OOC: Well I missed you guys, (espeacially you Yan:).

BIC:
Megatron after seeing most of his troops enter decided to follow suit,
he neared the repair bays, and noticed Ragnus for the first time. His
face turned to a look of suprise, "Who, Who are you?" he asked, curious
of this robot.

Speedbreaker walked up to the edge of the forest, and looked on a few
miles to the new Maximal city, Megatron wouldnt like this, he thought to
himself. He sat down, and kept watch.

Wildrider and Motormaster arrived back at base, both transformed.
Wildrider pulled out Beastbox's damaged cassette form. "He'll need
repairs" Wildrider noted. Motormaster smacked him in the back of the
head, "How percetpive moron" he hissed.

Sinnertwin landed between them, and sat down, letting his repair system
heal him.



Beachcomber and Cliffjumper walked up to Firedrill's cr chambered, and
opened it up. "Welcome back to the land of the livin" Cliffjumper said
with a smirk. Firedrill groaned, and stood up. "Well, how did I do
Jumper?" He asked. "Not bad, pretty good job, of course the Maximals
didnt help you much" He commented angrily. "Come on," Beachcomber said
in a soft tone, "We dont know what kind of situations and stress they
have been under." Cliffjumper began to look around with discust, "Well
with how seriously those lieutenants took the battle, I wouldnt be
suprised if theyve been on the defensive for a while. Bunch of rookies"
he said discustfully.
